    "body": "I've answered my own question, this is not a bug.\n\nI can do multiline statements if I use `\"\"\"` for the multi-line string and the `\\` at the end of the lines:\n\n```toml\n[custom.multi_line]\ncommand = \"\"\"\n    if ($true) { \\\n        echo '✅' \\\n    }\n\"\"\"\nwhen = true\nsymbol = 'm: '\nstyle = 'bold red'\nos = 'windows'\n```",
